article_title: With Obamacare and Skid Row, The Biggest Challenge May Be Trust
article_text:
Los Angeles, CA (90026)

Today

Areas of morning fog with some patchy drizzle. Cloudy early with partial sunshine expected late. High 68F. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy during the evening followed by cloudy skies overnight. Areas of fog developing with patchy drizzle possible. Low 54F. Winds WSW at 5 to 10 mph.
